ubstackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83d9888a-3fe5-4e53-95e8-822e24c5a607_1318x450.png" width="1318" height="450" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/83d9888a-3fe5-4e53-95e8-822e24c5a607_1318x450.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:450,&quot;width&quot;:1318,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:111468,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83d9888a-3fe5-4e53-95e8-822e24c5a607_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83d9888a-3fe5-4e53-95e8-822e24c5a607_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83d9888a-3fe5-4e53-95e8-822e24c5a607_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83d9888a-3fe5-4e53-95e8-822e24c5a607_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>按通货膨胀调整后的计算，制造业工资在过去二十年中相当平稳，但弗吉尼亚生产工人的收入比 2010 年<em>要少</em>。当安东尼唱“你的美元不是狗屎”时，他可能没有赚到一些金甲虫/比特币参考——他正在谈论他的社会阶层的人们近年来所经历的购买力的真正侵蚀。</p><p>从绝对值来看，每小时工资 24.62 美元，乘以每周 40 小时工作时间和每年 50 周工作时间，等于税前收入 49,240 美元。这高于个人收入中位数（包括不工作的人），但低于 2022 年工资中位数<a href="https://www.firstrepublic.com/insights-education/how-much-does-the-average-american-make">54,132 美元</a>。这是一份几乎肯定比一般职业更累、更无聊、更肮脏、更危险的工作。另外，请记住 24.62 美元/小时。是弗吉尼亚州工厂工人的<em>平均</em>工资，这意味着超过一半的工人的收入<em>低于</em>这个数字。</p><p>顺便说一句，矿工——安东尼说他希望政客们能够关注这一点——的表现比工厂工人要好一些。他们的工资比全国平均水平高出20%左右。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3d4b7777-2397-4882-9673-d9a37109dde2_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3d4b7777-2397-4882-9673-d9a37109dde2_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3d4b7777-2397-4882-9673-d9a37109dde2_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3d4b7777-2397-4882-9673-d9a37109dde2_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3d4b7777-2397-4882-9673-d9a37109dde2_1318x450.png" width="1318" height="450" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-pos