一起</a>，这一比例约为 20% 1990年为12%。考虑到这一点，并将同居夫妇与已婚夫妇相同计算，年轻人的住房拥有率可能比90年代<a href="https://twitter.com/john_voorheis/status/1691136966908063756">低3个百分点</a>。如果同居者不计算为已婚，那就是降低了 5 个百分点。不过，差异并不大，而且自 2010 年代中期以来的趋势线非常积极。）</p><p>作为结尾，让我恼火的一件事是，美国住房体系的运作方式使得<em>无论房价和抵押贷款利率发生什么变化</em>都很容易抱怨。如果房价上涨，你可以抱怨年轻人买房有多难。但如果房价下跌，你可以抱怨中产阶级的财富正在被摧毁（因为大多数美国中产阶级的大部分财富都在他们的房子里）。无论发生什么，你都可以讲述一个负面的故事。这是美国很早就选择将房地产作为中产阶级主要财富工具的产物，而不是像日本那样的股票和债券。但无论如何，我希望那些抱怨这些事情的人能够想象一下他们理想的房价状况是什么样的。</p><h4> 3.人工智能与经济增长的精彩辩论</h4><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-462">阅读更多</a></p>; 
Why skilled immigration (usually) benefits both countriesWhen to worry about brain drain, and when not to worry. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-skilled-immigration-usually-benefits https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-skilled-immigration-usually-benefitsNoah Smith Sun, 13 Aug 2023 06:37:20 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd0f65c73-3dd1-4c55-9402-53a957ab9c97_1024x438.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd0f65c73-3dd1-4c55-9402-53a957ab9c97_1024x438.jpeg" width="1024" height="438" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d0f65c73-3dd1-4c55-9402-53a957ab9c97_1024x438.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:438,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:72985,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd0f65c73-3dd1-4c55-9402-53a957ab9c97_1024x438.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd0f65c73-3dd1-4c55-9402-53a957ab9c97_1024x438.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_aut