"I'm cute I'm punk rock"A guest post by Pourteaux. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/im-cute-im-punk-rock https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/im-cute-im-punk-rockNoah Smith Sat, 12 Aug 2023 06:22:46 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F92e79fd4-0333-468f-aacf-18681ab8b8e3_2949x2564.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F92e79fd4-0333-468f-aacf-18681ab8b8e3_2949x2564.jpeg" width="1456" height="1266" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/92e79fd4-0333-468f-aacf-18681ab8b8e3_2949x2564.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1266,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F92e79fd4-0333-468f-aacf-18681ab8b8e3_2949x2564.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F92e79fd4-0333-468f-aacf-18681ab8b8e3_2949x2564.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F92e79fd4-0333-468f-aacf-18681ab8b8e3_2949x2564.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F92e79fd4-0333-468f-aacf-18681ab8b8e3_2949x2564.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">这篇文章中的所有照片均由作者本人拍摄。</figcaption></figure></div><p><em>这是您周末的一些轻松读物！对于那些不知道的人，我每年大约发表两次关于亚文化的帖子——基本上是一些业余的民族志。到目前为止，我已经完成了<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/tankies">坦克</a>、<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/weebs?s=w">微博</a>、<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/zines">杂志</a>和<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/ai-techies">人工智能技术</a>。问题是，最终我会用完我足够了解的亚文化来写。所以我开始征集客座亚文化帖子。</em></p><p><em>这篇文章由 Pourteaux (Dennis Porto) 提交，<a href="https://read.pourteaux.xyz/p/im-cute-im-punk-rock">最初发布在他自己的博客上</a>，您当然应该<a href="https://read.pourteaux.xyz/">查看</a>该博客。这是一种奇怪的、极具讽刺意味的、某种政治右派（或者可能只是虚无主义）亚文化的写照，这种亚文化几年前起源于纽约一个名为 Dimes Square 的小社区，后来传播到互联网上。 Pourteaux 开始有点痴迷于详细记录这种亚文化，认为它是 2020 年代对 1970 年代原始朋克摇滚运动的呼应。由于我自己的个人论点之一是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-new-1970s">2020 年代是新的 70 年代</a>，所以我显然对这种解释很感兴趣。无论如何，看看你的想法！如果您希望我写或请客人写其他亚文化，请随时留下任何建议。</em></p><div><hr></div><p> 20 世纪 70 年代的朋克摇滚运动发生在社会动荡的顶峰时期，越南战争、民权运动、妇女解放和水门事件就是体现。朋克摇滚作为一种反文化是这个不和谐时代的自然反映，朋克摇滚乐手不遗余力地表明他们对社会规范的拒绝。例如，艺术评论家丹·格雷厄姆（Dan Graham）在<a href="https://twitter.com/pourteaux/status/1644698595470311426?s=20">他的文章</a>《自由主义的终结》中谈到了这一现象，描述了朋克摇滚如何讽刺性地使用纳粹标志等法西斯形象或居民乐队的“<a href="https://www.residents.com/historical/?page=thirdreichandroll">第三帝国卷</a>”等专辑标题作为对自由主义的强烈拒绝。 “‘成熟’的幻想让人回想起 60 年代的‘美好氛围’。”这些禁忌暗示不出所料地引起了上流社会的谴责，朋克摇滚乐手们陶醉在他们新发现的恶名中，并计划着他们的下一次表演越轨行为。</p><p>作家兼经济学家诺亚·史密斯<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-new-1970s?utm_source=profile&amp;utm_medium=reader2">将我们当前的社会时刻比</a>作“新 20 世纪 70 年代”，并且恰如其分地出现了一种具有类似越界反馈循环的新亚文化，我将其称为“前 Dimes Square 文化”，以纽约命名。城市微型社区于 2020 年开始发展。Dimes 广场距离曼哈顿东村的朋克摇滚发源地仅几站地铁。众所周知，Dimes Square 街区被过度分析了：它是<a href="https://thebaffler.com/latest/escape-from-dimes-square-harrison">无数</a>关于其街道、餐馆和少数小名人的三角地带的<a href="https://spikeartmagazine.com/?q=articles/dimes-square-spiral">曝光</a>的主题。总而言之，钱币广场是唐人街的一个非官方微型社区，从 2020 年到 2021 年，它培养了自己的声誉（取决于你问的是谁），要么是后政治前卫行家，要么不那么仁慈地成为时尚讽刺的反动分子。这是一种亚文化，其成员本身有时会感到不安，当地一家卡巴拉专门书店的服务员告诉我，即使是“Dimes”餐厅（广场由此得名）的供应商也不愿使用这个绰号而是选择“唐人街”的官方名称。 </p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/97583d71-3060-47fb-bbea-599447ad1b54_2949x2564.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0dc6bbbb-ba41-4174-a8a8-144d7248db5f_3024x4032.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7b48d419-cc81-4f4e-a830-2711afabca79_1067x1500.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;A summer evening in New York City's Dimes Square. As the neighborhood gentrified, its trangression-centric subculture found viral infamy online.&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a76e1aa7-3f12-41b7-899e-df9deafe7127_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p>钱币广场的场景有几个定义性的人物和一个自我参照的神话。逆向“红色恐慌”<a href="https://redscarepodcast.libsyn.com/">播客</a>中的女演员达莎·内克拉索娃（Dasha Nekrasova）以及她在自由派媒体中的多次露面（《纽约时报》在一篇描述新兴“逆向美学[及其对天主教的拥抱”的文章中<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2022/08/09/opinion/nyc-catholicism-dimes-square-religion.html">评论了</a>她新发现的天主教信仰），还有《纽约客》（她与被赦免的重罪犯和特朗普助手罗杰·斯通一起参加的<a href="https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2023/03/27/roger-stone-shakes-a-nixonian-martini">聚会</a>），还有索菲亚·范德比尔特（ <a href="https://twitter.com/alivegirl001101">Sophia Vanderbilt</a> ），她是一位非常在线的社交名流，为 Milady Maker NFT 做出了贡献，还有一份已经停业的独立报纸《醉运河》（Drunken Canal）附近的运河街，以及以“有人请哥伦拜整个醉酒的运河编辑人员”等帖子而闻名的<a href="https://cashedcobrazhousewriter.substack.com/">angelicism01</a>精神分裂风格博客，以及作家奥诺·利维和选角导演沃尔特·皮尔斯，他们共同主持了“<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/bh/podcast/wet-brain/id1581669864">湿脑</a>”播客。 </p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/135fb0de-2e30-48c4-a8a3-3c9baa689b77_2048x1536.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/44543f34-dcfa-4674-9bd2-5029eaa14fee_900x675.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/139f7a97-40e3-4d69-9775-50126ca1279b_1536x2048.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Dimes Square jolts alive at night, every day of the week. Major streets are closed to traffic, prioritizing local revelers. Several popular spots eschew any signage, like Kiki's: a Greek restaurant that continues to display the signs from the prior Chinatown printing tenet.&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/86b243f6-1070-42cc-9078-4d29872cbbd2_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p> Dimes Square 的场景在 2020 年打破封锁的派对中达到顶峰，但随着新冠疫情后租金价格上涨（甚至豪华酒店开业），该场景的许多核心创意类型搬回了布鲁克林。一些文化评论家甚至宣布这场运动已经死亡。现实情况是，钱币广场一直是街区文化和互联网文化的融合，随着街区的高档化，网络部分成为了主导组成部分。事实上，我的估计是，网络上的“前 Dimes Square”文化的影响远远超过了街区本身。这种从微社区到病毒式的、不断变化的在线艺术运动的飞跃是本文的基础。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg" width="574" height="574" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1456,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:574,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Image" title="图像" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb456314f-b5bb-42cc-b318-e2ea082c92c7_2048x2048.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">关于 Dimes Square 的文章已经太多了（照片来自<a href="https://twitter.com/deankissick/status/1589350575363461120">Dean Kissick</a> ）。</figcaption></figure></div><p>即使是这次 Dimes 广场的旋风之旅也凸显了这种新兴亚文化的一些主题。不敬和越轨是至关重要的：红色恐慌和天使主义01随意使用贬义词“弱智”，似乎只是为了提醒你，他们不遵守现行规范。红色恐慌的共同主持人讽刺地称对方为“法西斯分子”并崇拜各种独裁者，但同时具有巨大的文化流畅性——讨论动漫系列<em>《新世纪福音战士》</em>的弗洛伊德主题或最近的政治事件（例如，“CNN 小丑厅”） 。具有讽刺意味的是，人们对宗教的信仰，尤其是天主教。皈依天主教的人将其视为“我的天主教弧线”，或者说是“上帝赋予的”。匿名的anglecism01博客号召编辑人员像“哥伦拜恩”一样，采用了典型的“精神分裂”风格，这种风格虽然迷人且充满诗意，但也让人感觉难以接近。这种亚文化也是极其自我参照的：有一小部分人物不断地自我引用，仿佛是为了强化他们自己的“传说”或邻里神话。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png" width="564" height="312.60164835164835" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:807,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:564,&quot;bytes&quot;:1826651,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5473c024-54ae-46a8-91c7-f7f5ad6ec91d_2402x1332.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> Angelicism01 博客对最初的 Dimes Square 文化产生了影响，并继续激发纽约市出现的新的在线和去中心化迭代。</figcaption></figure></div><p> Angelicism01 因<a href="https://cashedcobrazhousewriter.substack.com/p/a-note-on-the-vibe-shift-vs-the-discord">推广</a>“氛围转变”新词而闻名，该词指的是 2021 年 6 月的几天，其支持者声称，不仅在 Dimes Square 场景中发生了文化转变，而且在整个互联网上也发生了文化转变。事实上， <a href="https://remilia.org/">Remilia Collective</a> （Milady Maker 和其他艺术项目背后的组织）将这种氛围转变描述为“当代文化中激进支点的现象，几乎是立即自我组织的，没有由一小群密切参与的海报进行的单一特定催化剂——这种现象只有网络时代才有可能。”随后，主要媒体（例如《纽约杂志》的<a href="https://www.thecut.com/2022/02/a-vibe-shift-is-coming.html">The Cut</a> ）报道了这种氛围转变，引起 Dimes Square 的小名人们的关注，同时争论谁被引用、没有被引用以及氛围转变发生的确切日期。 </p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/dd970893-1cf0-4bbc-8eb1-2c397bb6bb03_2316x3088.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ccaf074c-0c4c-4675-b303-ded61d7aee0c_4032x3024.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/408edeb2-3dd7-4ced-ab2f-6a623c3f09cc_1290x1915.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;The author at New York City's \&quot;Milady Rave\&quot; in June 2023. 2hollis performed (highly recommended). The Praxis Society (a Network State startup backed by Peter Thiel) was a co-sponsor. The venue was a short walk from Dimes Square.&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/86bc5f91-1b32-4105-9afa-6684bcd65ebb_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p> <a href="https://remilia.org/">Remilia Collective</a>以其 2021 年夏季推出的<a href="https://twitter.com/miladymaker">Milady Maker</a> NFT 系列而闻名，该系列一直是忠实粉丝的源泉，继熟悉的朋克摇滚越界反馈循环之后，也引发了一波又一波的争议和<a href="https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2022/05/24/milady-nft-prices-tumble-after-creator-doxxes-self-as-person-behind-controversial-miya/">取消</a>。 Milady NFT 是可爱的动漫头像，通过例如讽刺性地引用<a href="https://dl.openseauserdata.com/cache/originImage/files/9297f26dc0a6f636c39353a8f69889fe.png">9-11</a>或日本“ <a href="https://dl.openseauserdata.com/cache/originImage/files/83e09e939089b6ac7fe7a051b3e55534.png">蛰居族</a>”的 incel 文化概念来调情。乍一看，这些图像可能显得轻松且简单，但该项目具有巨大的深度。例如，angelicism01（曾经是前 Dimes Square 文化的精神灵感）在兰迪安加速主义的背景下<a href="https://cashedcobrazhousewriter.substack.com/p/no-milady-nfts-not-now-the-return">分析了</a>Milady 项目。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png" width="545" height="664.7681451612904" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1210,&quot;width&quot;:992,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:545,&quot;bytes&quot;:1480734,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc411cbc7-ef5b-4326-8ffb-061aa367a5bb_992x1210.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 帮助推动了 Milady 项目的主流关注。</figcaption></figure></div><p>除了图像本身之外，还有一种蓬勃发展的互联网文化，即发帖者“佩戴”米拉迪的个人资料照片并寻求病毒式传播（通常会成功）、大队帖子，并以个人资料图片中女孩的声音讽刺地发帖。多年来，成员们对他们的各种“取消”有一定的感情，具有讽刺意味的是，他们自我认同为“恋童美容师支持厌食症死亡邪教”，尽管他们对这些领域的倾向似乎大多是表演性的和自我神话。尽管对于休闲的网络冲浪者来说可能不会立即显而易见，但这是一种作为图像集合的延伸的在线行为艺术。 </p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/41baf621-a034-41f7-8ae4-223e43c2a309_1000x1250.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8c524f92-d56c-4d37-b3d0-c868f085d408_1000x1250.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;From the Milady Maker collection (Remilia, 2021).&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b63d93e9-0bf2-40cf-aa13-8debcb07fca2_1456x720.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p>与其纠缠于 Milady NFT（就像 Dimes Square 一样，已经写得太多了），最近有一个名为<a href="https://schizoposters.xyz/">SchizoPosters</a>的衍生作品，它在这个不断发展的亚文化中提出了新概念。 SchizoPosters 遵循与 Milady NFT 相同的总体美学，但其重叠的文本和图表很大程度上来自阴谋论、神秘的、臭名昭著的 4chan 复制粘贴，以及来自各种 Discord 服务器和孵化这种文化的其他飞地的自我参照传说。这些文本和图表被其定义的精神分裂美学所覆盖，仿佛阴谋论者白板的一部分，在想象的概念和事件之间画出疯狂的箭头。例如， <a href="https://i.seadn.io/gcs/files/2b59616718685823468366436b794959.png?auto=format&amp;dpr=1&amp;w=2048">一张这样的</a>SchizoPoster 在右上角有 MP5 机枪的示意图，整个左侧覆盖着连接神秘学概念的箭头网（“撒旦教堂”、“L. Ron Hubbard”、“方舟”）盟约”）和阴谋（“51区”、“疫苗”、“孟山都”、“爬虫人”、“黑粘”），包括一些明显违法的参考文献（“锡安长老议定书”），以及右侧与各种 4chan 和 reddit copypastas（“一个女孩和一个玩家？……”）。 </p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3987973-93fd-46ef-a62b-d1ca145354eb_1440x2160.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/13c1c148-f7d6-41c4-ae34-00b974c0b6c3_1440x2160.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7b9a1f85-7c6b-4571-9810-e60f3e37170b_1440x2160.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;From the SchizoPosters collection (Radbro Webring, 2023).&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/cf24da5f-5e1f-4779-84b8-52938210434c_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p>这些图像的精神分裂美学令人着迷，每一张都邀请人们掉入兔子洞，从互联网分散的黑暗角落中发现大量的知识宝库。许多图像还倾向于东亚主题，并覆盖中文或日文文本。事实上，东亚主题成为这种亚文化最近迭代的中心焦点，称为“基础弱智帮派”或<a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%23%F0%9D%94%85%E2%84%9C%F0%9D%94%8A&amp;src=hashtag_click">#𝔅ℜ𝔊</a> 。这些海报并没有展示米拉迪或精神分裂海报的个人资料照片，而是呈现出一个真正的中国女孩的形象，通常借用中国社交媒体网站小红书的图片。 SchizoPosters 的艺术在于图像，而 BRG 完全是一种在线行为艺术。帖子再次通过疯狂宣称（“中国比西方领先 3000 年”，以及从 TikTok 借用的重庆风格视频）或打破常规（来自新疆的视频，“没有种族灭绝，只有爱”）而引发病毒式传播。 ”）。几乎从程序上讲，这些帖子引起了病毒般的恶名（“3000 年”的帖子有 2500 万次浏览，并被反中共账户转发），这要归功于愤怒的“规范者”与社区成员的争吵。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg" width="1456" height="957" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:957,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:254373,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F63eb4a6f-ad93-422a-87cd-27937e739cb3_1566x1029.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption"> “智障团伙”代表帖</figcaption></figure></div><p>智障团伙流行的另一个主题是“清丸”的概念。你可能读过<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Red_pill_and_blue_pill#:~:text=In%20The%20Matrix,-In%20the%20film&amp;text=Morpheus%20says%20%22You%20take%20the,deep%20the%20rabbit%20hole%20goes.%22">《黑客帝国》中流行的“选择红色药丸或蓝色药丸”的参考</a>，指的是在看到现实的本来面目（“红色”）或呈现在我们面前的世界令人安慰的天真之间的选择（“蓝色的”）。透明药丸是对社会混乱的彻底接受，其支持者认为这是比那些保持世俗关注的人更开明的观点。这种对混乱的拥抱，与未来东方主义相结合，是 BRG 式加速主义的基础。</p><p>加速主义是前 Dimes Square 思想中反复出现的主题，因为它是 Remilia 公司的<a href="https://goldenlight.mirror.xyz/o5CpltqerVga2ULwztI_jLmlpBe57K-ej2JWkVMJB14">基础</a>（特别是 kali-yuga 加速主义，或“kali/acc”），并且同样<a href="https://www.fastcompany.com/90756392/inside-remilia-corporation-the-anti-woke-dao-behind-the-doomed-milady-maker-nft">归因</a>于<a href="https://cashedcobrazhousewriter.substack.com/">天使主义01</a> 。<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Accelerationism">加速主义</a>有很多种，但一个流行的版本是这样的想法：克服我们当前（“<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strauss%E2%80%93Howe_generational_theory">第四次转折</a>”或“黑药丸”）社会崩溃的唯一方法是通过一场类似于二战或美国核弹的毁灭性灾难。内战。这些加速论者不仅承认这种灾难是不可避免的，而且<em>还推动</em>它更快地发生，以便我们能够“退出”到另一边的科技乌托邦。其他加速论者较少关注“通过灾难退出”，而是将技术进步视为救世主，迎来<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technological_singularity#:~:text=The%20technological%20singularity%E2%80%94or%20simply,of%20the%20singularity%20hypothesis%2C%20I.%20J.">奇点</a>。对于“Based Retard Gang”来说，乌托邦是一座闪闪发光的赛博朋克中国大城市，“领先西方 3000 年”。 </p><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e369d524-9747-4b74-bee2-c2f6ffa211c4_828x522.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d42e438b-2786-4b45-9331-d03e913ae95c_886x874.jpeg&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Clear pill ideology is an evolution of the accelerationism often attributed to reactionary rightists and tech contrarians.&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f1e6ec35-613e-423a-9c47-f92c0e59df59_1456x720.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p>从 Dimes Square 到 Base Retard Gang 的疯狂之路是一场不断变形和去中心化的艺术运动。唯一不变的似乎是旧朋克摇滚时代的越轨反馈循环：当你计划下一次越轨时，沐浴在规范的愤怒中。一些观察家对 Dimes 广场赞不绝口，他们的观点是对的，随着街区的高档化，许多原创创意人员已经离开。他们错过的是它作为一种超越的“<a href="https://goldenlight.mirror.xyz/JHeIf9ahizF3HXEL2XxIQfrqCyPdvtSp1P-AsWoHGr0">网络灵性</a>”在网上持久存在（事实上，它蓬勃发展）。虽然最初的 Dimes Square 团队中的一些人已经退出，但其他关键人物即使在这个数字原生迭代中仍然存在。就连我在 Base Retard Gang 中采访过的新人也将 Angelicism01 的原始帖子视为他们的“创作灵感”。蕾米莉亚 (Remilia) 狂欢现已在东京和巴黎举行，甚至还包括最近在 Minecraft 服务器上举办的仅限在线观看的“盛大舞会”（以经典的越轨风格），其中以模拟大规模枪击事件为特色。</p><p>前 Dimes Square 文化随着去中心化而日趋成熟。与该地区有联系的艺术家现在在纽约<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/03/17/t-magazine/josh-kline.html">顶级博物馆</a>展出。埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）正在<a href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1656326406618619910">发布</a>米拉迪表情包，格莱姆斯（Grimes）正在<a href="https://twitter.com/Grimezsz/status/1656440347499851776?s=20">整理</a>各种争议。甚至这篇文章也是对一种随心所欲的文化进行理性化的努力。随着它的成熟，讽刺本身可以更好地理解为“尝试”不同的加速主义哲学的方式，并具有合理的否认性，而不是纯粹的表演。</p><p>这种艺术很诱人，就像朋克摇滚一样，即使是我们这些沉浸在“规范核心”情感中的人也可以在道德上享受它。然而，从 20 世纪 70 年代开始，表演性越轨就面临着一个富有启发性的挑战：并不是每个人都理解朋克摇滚乐手及其法西斯意象的讽刺意义，当真正的新法西斯光头党出现时，该运动必须进行反击（例如，通过诸如 Clash 和 Sham 的“Rock against Racism”之类的努力）。当然，这种调节努力打破了越界反馈循环，对于朋克摇滚来说，它在 20 世纪 80 年代将其风格淡化为更被社会接受的“新浪潮”流派。唉，对于那些寻求掠夺兔子洞深处、实现网络灵性或对此感到愤怒的人来说，我们仍然牢牢地停留在前 Dimes Square 亚文化的 70 年代弧线上。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa17de9a2-f48a-4990-936e-ba62a9ca0120_995x762.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa17de9a2-f48a-4990-936e-ba62a9ca0120_995x762.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa17de9a2-f48a-4990-936e-ba62a9ca0120_995x762.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa17de9a2-f48a-4990-936e-ba62a9ca0120_995x762.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa17de9a2-f48a-4990-936e-ba62a9ca0120_995x762.png" width="995" height="762" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot